{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回「飞刀与快剑」。风雪交加的冰天雪地中，李寻欢驾马车南行，途中遇见一位孤独倔强的少年（阿飞），邀其上车被拒。少年腰间插着一柄简陋铁剑，自尊心极强，不愿接受施舍。李寻欢对少年产生了浓厚兴趣。二人先后来到风雪小镇的客栈，客栈中金狮镖局的急风剑诸葛雷正在吹嘘镖局威风。此时黄河黑道上臭名昭著的碧血双蛇（白蛇与黑蛇）闯入客栈，逼抢诸葛雷从口外带回的黄布包袱。赵老二被黑蛇一剑斩首，诸葛雷被迫当众爬地求饶。少年挺身而出挑战白蛇，以五十两银子为赌注比剑，一剑刺穿白蛇咽喉。黑蛇惊恐逃遁。诸葛雷趁少年不备偷袭，却被李寻欢以刻木小刀（飞刀）刺入咽喉而死。少年与李寻欢以酒结缘，故事拉开序幕。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人生本就充满了矛盾，任何人都无可奈何。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "天已快黑了，前面的路还很远，少爷你快上车吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种天气，想不到竟还有人要在冰天雪地里奔波受苦，我想他一定是很孤独，很可怜的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "上车来，我载你一段路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你是聋子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "原来你不是聋子，那么就上来喝口酒吧，一口酒对任何人都不会有害处的！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我喝不起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "我请你喝酒，用不着你花钱买。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不是我自己买来的东西，我绝不要，不是我自己买来的酒，我也绝不喝……我的话已经说得够清楚了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "够清楚了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "好，我走。但等你买得起酒的时候，你肯请我喝一杯么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，我请你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "你可曾见过如此奇怪的少年么？我本来以为他必定已饱经沧桑，谁知他说起话却那么天真，那么老实。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他只不过是个倔强的孩子而已。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "你可瞧见他腰带上插着的那柄剑么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那也能算是一柄剑么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "依我看来，那也只不过是个小孩子的玩具而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "依我看来，这玩具却危险得很，还是莫要去玩它的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "南面的上房已空出来了，也已打扫干净，少爷随时都可以休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "金狮镖局也有人住在这客栈里，像是刚从口外押镖回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "哦？押镖的是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就是那'急风剑'诸葛雷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "这狂徒，居然能活到现在，倒也不容易。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那孩子的脚程不快，只怕要等到起更时才能赶到这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "text": "我看他也不是走不快，只不过是不肯浪费体力而已，你看见过一匹狼在雪地上走路么？假如前面没有它的猎物，后面又没有追兵，它一定不肯走快的，因为它觉得光将力气用在走路上，未免太可惜了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "虬髯大汉",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但那孩子却并不是一匹狼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_zhao_lao_er",
      "text": "老二，你还记得那天咱们在太行山下遇见'太行四虎'的事么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "赵老二",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "俺怎么不记得？那天'太行四虎'竟敢来动大哥保的那批红货，四个人耀武扬威，还说什么'只要你诸葛雷在地上爬一圈，咱们兄弟立刻放你过山，否则咱们非但要留下你的红货，还要留下你的脑袋。'",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "镖师三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "谁知他们的刀还未砍下，大哥的剑已刺穿了他们的喉咙。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "赵老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是俺赵老二吹牛，若论掌力之雄厚，自然得数咱们的总镖头'金狮掌'，但若论剑法之快，当今天下只怕再也没有人比得上咱们大哥了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "两位高姓大名？恕在下眼拙……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "你就是'急风剑'诸葛雷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "不……不敢。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "就凭你，也配称急风剑？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "留下你从口外带回来的那包东西，就饶你的命！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "赵老二",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "两位只怕是弄错了，咱们这趟镖是在口外交的货，现在镖车已空了，什么东西都没有，两位……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "两位的招子果然亮，咱们这次的确从口外带了包东西回来，但两位就想这么样带走，只怕还办不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "你想怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "两位好歹总得留两手真功夫下来，叫在下回去也好有个交待。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "只要两位能照样玩一手，我立刻就将这包东西奉上，否则就请两位走吧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "这只能算是厨子的手艺，也能算武功么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "两位莫非就是……就是碧血双蛇么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "你还是认出了我们，总算眼睛还没有瞎。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛雷",
      "listener": "char_hei_she",
      "text": "既然是两位看上了这包东西，在下还有什么话好说的，两位就请……就请拿去吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_lei",
      "text": "你若肯在地上爬一圈，咱们兄弟立刻就放你走，否则咱们非但要留下你的包袱，还要留下你的脑袋。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这人脾气已变了，难怪他能活到现在。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "原来此地竟还有高人，我兄弟倒险些看走眼了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_she",
      "speaker_name": "黑蛇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这包袱是人家情愿送给咱们的，只要有人的剑法比我兄弟更快，我兄弟也情愿将这包袱双手奉上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要有比我兄弟更快的剑，我兄弟非但将这包袱送给他，连脑袋也送给他！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "你的脑袋能值几两银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "方才那句话是你说的么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你想买我的脑袋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "我只想知道它能值几两银子，因为我要将它卖给你自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_she",
      "speaker_name": "白蛇",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "卖给我自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_bai_she",
      "text": "不错，因为我既不想要这包袱，也不想要这脑袋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
